data.name: BBQ Chicken Nachos
data.quickTastyDescription: Crispy tortilla chips topped with tender BBQ chicken, melted cheese, and zesty toppings for a crowd-pleasing snack!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a mixing bowl, combine the shredded chicken with BBQ sauce until well coated.
Spread a layer of tortilla chips on a large baking tray.
Evenly distribute the BBQ chicken over the tortilla chips.
Sprinkle shredded cheddar cheese generously over the chicken and chips.
Place the baking tray in the oven and bake for about 10-15 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.
Remove from the oven and top with sour cream, sliced green onions, and jalapeños if desired. Serve immediately.
